## Category Design Workflow

- [ ] 1. Identify category opportunity: Find an underserved or poorly defined space
- [ ] 2. Define the category: Name it, scope it, establish its rules
- [ ] 3. Build the brand-category bond: Make the brand synonymous with the category
- [ ] 4. Educate the market: Create demand for the category itself
- [ ] 5. Defend the category: Build moats against competitors
- [ ] 6. Grow the category: Expand total addressable market

## Key Inputs
- Brand: {{brand_name}}
- Current market: {{current_market}}
- Category opportunity: {{category_opportunity}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
